OL,5, The family of Leonard Bernstein have   
OL,6, defended actor Bradley Cooper in a row 
OL,7, over his biopic of the late composer.  
OL,9,FThe first trailer for Maestro, which   
OL,10,FCooper both directs and stars in, was  
OL,11,Freleased earlier this week.            
OL,13,FIt attracted some criticism over the   
OL,14,Fsize of Cooper's nose, which some      
OL,15,Fsocial media users said played up to   
OL,16,Foffensive Jewish stereotypes.          
OL,18,FBut Bernstein's family said they were  
OL,19,F"perfectly fine" with Cooper using     
OL,20,Fmake-up to "amplify" his appearance.   
